user_question: average listening minutes of active users in last two days on day to day basis
sql_query:
SELECT 
    DATE(date_tz) AS listening_date,
    AVG(mins_listened) AS average_minutes_listened
FROM 
    analytics.super.raw_listening_impression_combined_show_level
WHERE 
    final_profile_id IN (
        SELECT final_profile_id 
        FROM analytics.super.premium_user_all_orders 
        WHERE subscription_status = 'active'
    )
    AND date_tz >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '2 days'
    AND date_tz < CURRENT_DATE
GROUP BY 
    listening_date
ORDER BY 
    listening_date;
